<br>
Guilds usually reserve it for 2-3 days at a time.  Everquest Raids is a good place to do it.  It would be polite to reserve a time.  You might just note that you are just doing 7th island.<br>
<br>
Also if a guild is starting their Sky raid the same time you are on the 7th island, its not likely to be a problem.  It takes 2-3 days to get there anyway.<br>
<br>
Also clearing the 7th island isn't likely to cause a problem for people.  If you haven't done the previous island and spawned the big bad mob on this island, you won't be able to spawn Sirran.  That would be the one thing that could screw up an existing raid because if Sirran is spawned on one island he can't be spawned on another.  But the way the 7th island is done its not possible if you just port up to 7th island.<br>
<br>
People park toons up there for crown farming all the time.  I'm just outlining how you would go about doing it so perhaps all mages can get their crown without paying 60k.  You don't have to be an uber guild to do this.  Just find a guild to help you park people up there for a long time <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Izarek<br>
